data.description: This wonderful home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a Saltwater Pool in the highly popular Countryside Estates! Walk into the large living room with 18 feet high ceilings and a cozy fireplace This spacious kitchen with SS appliances has a great view of the pool. The Primary room is down and features a large bathroom with dual sinks, garden jacuzzi tub, separate shower and a walk-in closet. When you walk outside, you will be greeted with a cozy backyard and sparking pool that has a heated spa. Relax on the covered patio that is perfect for the whole family to enjoy. This home also comes with water sprinkler system for those hot Summers.  This home is located in the Grapevine-Colleyville ISD. This home is located close to schools, shopping, restaurants and DFW Airport. Updates include: HVAC April 2023, Pool resurfacing March 2023, and pool pump replaced in May 2022. Come see this home as it won't last long! Buyer and buyers agent to verify measurements and schools.
